      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 42.8 - 老子 42.9</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 42.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>唯孤﹑寡﹑不穀，而王公以為稱。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What men dislike is to be orphans, to have little virtue, to be as carriages without naves;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
